<h4><a href="https://twitter.com/themandalorian/status/1301157958819045376">《曼达洛人》第二季回归时间确定</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363323" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/intro-1596487723.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="561" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/intro-1596487723.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/intro-1596487723-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/intro-1596487723-768x431.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>官方宣布，第二季《曼达洛人》将于 10 月 30 日在 Disney+ 上线。</p>
<p>据此前报道，在《曼达洛人》之外，迪士尼还为 Disney+ 打造其它「星战」电视剧，其中包括一部由 Ewan McGregor 回归饰演欧比旺・克诺比的剧集，以及一部围绕《侠盗一号》中卡西安・安多的剧集。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
